songs.title: The Meaning
songs.lyrics:
The music placed on this CD is recognized as having various supernatural abiilites
Including personal sacrifice for the purpose to make contact with natural spiritual forces to help guide people to reach their full potential
The music placed in this medicine bag may also contain songs that are meaningful due to a personal experience
The contents are for your spiritual strength only
The power on this disc may also include increasing hunting abilities, aiding fighting skills, healing allies, and hindering enemies
